steps.name: Check out code into the Go module directory
Determine if PR is from external contributor
steps.run:
if [ "${{ github.event.pull_request.head.repo.full_name }}" = "${{ github.repository }}" ]; then
echo "is_external=false" >> $GITHUB_OUTPUT
else
echo "is_external=true" >> $GITHUB_OUTPUT
fi

steps.name: Test
steps.run:
if [ "${{ steps.pr_check.outputs.is_external }}" = "true" ]; then
  go test -v -tags=external ./...
else
  go test -v ./...
fi
